name: write
description: Print <obj> to the screen in machine-readable form.

name: display
description: Print <obj> to the screen in human-readable form.

name: newline
description: Print a newline to the screen. Equivalent to: (display "\n")

name: read
description: Read an EScheme datum as input from the keyboard.

name: read-string
description:
Read an EScheme datum from the string. Returns a pair:
  (cons <read-datum> <str-w/o-serialized-read-datum>)
